  "text": "The acute insulin response was calculated as the mean incremental insulin concentration during the 8-min IVGTT, where the mean was determined by trapezoidal integration. Analogous indices were obtained using C-peptide concentration and insulin secretion, which was calculated by deconvolution from C-peptide concentration [CITATION_1] .",
